    {
      "instruction": "<p>Trim, then slice the <strong>spring onions</strong> lengthways into batons</p><p>Deseed the<strong> pepper<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> </strong>(scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and cut into thin strips</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
