      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken has browned, add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong>,<strong> ginger paste</strong>, <strong>spring onion batons </strong>and <strong>sliced</strong> <strong>pepper</strong> to the pan and cook for 4-5 min or until beginning to soften and the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
      "order": 5,
